include ../menu/wallet.jade
section.panel.wide.content(ng-controller="SecurityCtrl")
  p.important(rp-l10n) Your money and wallet are protected digitally through encryption algorithms that can be unlocked&nbsp;
    b(rp-l10n-inc) only with your personal keys
  ul.notices
    li(rp-l10n) – No one else has them, so don't lose them!
    li(rp-l10n) – Never share them!
  .title
    .icon.wallet
    .name(rp-l10n) Wallet Key
    .more
      span(rp-l10n) {{userBlob.data.contacts.length}} contacts,&nbsp;
        span {{enc.length | rpfilesize}} &ensp;
    .more
      span(rp-download='enc',rp-download-filename='ripple-wallet.txt', rp-l10n)
        | You can&nbsp;
        a(rp-download-trigger) backup your wallet to a file
        | .
  ul.description(ng-hide="showKeys")
    li(rp-l10n) This is the key you use every time you use ripple.
    li(rp-l10n) You created it when you chose your Wallet Name and Passphrase.
    li(rp-l10n) It protects your money, your contacts and account history.
    li
      b(rp-l10n) Never forget it, never share it.
  div
    .infoBox(ng-show="showKeys")
      .part
        span.label(rp-l10n) Wallet name:
        span.value {{userCredentials.username}}
      .part
        span.label(rp-l10n) Pass Phrase:
        span.value(ng-show="passUnmask") {{userCredentials.password}}
        span.value(ng-hide="passUnmask") {{userCredentials.password | rpmask}}
        rp-confirm(
          action-text="Are you in a safe place, where no person, or camera can see your screen?"
          action-button-text="Yes, show me"
          action-function="passUnmask=true"
          cancel-button-text="No"
          ng-hide="passUnmask")
            a(ng-hide="passUnmask", rp-l10n) Show
        a(ng-click="passUnmask=false", ng-show="passUnmask", rp-l10n) Hide
  .hint(ng-show="showKeys", rp-l10n) This gives access to your wallet. DO NOT SHARE THIS WITH ANYONE. Keep it safe. Keep it private.

  .title
    .icon.money
    .name(rp-l10n) Secret Key
  ul.description(ng-hide="showKeys")
    li(rp-l10n) This key is for emergency use only. You did not choose it. The network created it. You don't have to memorize it.
    li(rp-l10n) The Secret Key accesses Your money, which is already contained inside your wallet.
    li(rp-l10n) But if you ever lose your wallet, you can recover just your money with this key.
    li
      b(rp-l10n) Store it somewhere safe, never share it.
  div
    .infoBox(ng-show="showKeys")
      .part
        span.value(ng-show="SecretKeyUnmask") {{userCredentials.master_seed}}
        span.value(ng-hide="SecretKeyUnmask") {{userCredentials.master_seed | rpmask}}
      rp-confirm(
        action-text="Are you in a safe place, where no person, or camera can see your screen?"
        action-button-text="Yes, show me"
        action-function="SecretKeyUnmask=true"
        cancel-button-text="No"
        ng-hide="SecretKeyUnmask")
          a(ng-hide="SecretKeyUnmask") Show
      a(ng-click="SecretKeyUnmask=false", ng-show="SecretKeyUnmask") Hide
  .hint(ng-show="showKeys", rp-l10n) This gives access to your money. DO NOT SHARE THIS WITH ANYONE. Keep it safe. Keep it private.

  button.btn.btn-info.show-keys(ng-click="showKeys=true", ng-hide="showKeys", rp-l10n) Show my keys